# 
# Resume-Maker - Environment Setup
# 
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to exactly `.env`
# 2. Replace the placeholder values below with your actual keys.
# Note: Your actual `.env` file is ignored by Git and will remain local/secret.

# 1. Google Gemini API Key (Required)
# You can generate a free API key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_actual_google_ai_studio_api_key_here

# not using serperdevtool but if you decide to add tools like SerperDevTool back in later, 
# you can leave a placeholder for it here:
# SERPER_API_KEY=your_serper_api_key_here
